  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the World of Magic Cats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I am Magic Cat, and during my adventurous explorations, I discovered this mysterious magical spring.<br>The spring is surrounded by many obstacles, and I need your help to overcome these barriers and reach the magical waters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a casual puzzle game with unlimited gameplay featuring hundreds of levels, with more being designed for future updates. When facing challenges, players can easily obtain helpful items in-game or exchange them using cookies.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3305360/extras/dd3c5cfe8010e1f37c3ec9bf639ac1e3.avif?t=1741347355\" width=512 height=512 /></span></p>",
